<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 03:14:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>降息押注增强，亚洲股市上涨；欧洲央行成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-06/</link><description>由于对美联储可能在 9 月份降息的预期不断上升，亚洲股市周四上涨，而欧元在欧洲央行政策会议之前上涨，市场普遍预期降息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 02:32:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲央行决定前欧元稳定，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-steadies-ahead-ecb-decision-dollar-dips-2024-06-06/</link><description>周四，在欧洲央行 (ECB) 做出政策决定之前，欧元走强，交易员认为降息几乎是板上钉钉的事，而美元因对美联储今年预计将实行宽松周期的新押注而走软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 01:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-steadies-ahead-ecb-decision-dollar-dips-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚、中国寻求与所罗门群岛建立更紧密的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-china-seek-bigger-ties-with-solomon-islands-2024-06-06/</link><description>澳大利亚外交部长黄英贤表示，堪培拉希望与其太平洋邻国所罗门群岛以及一个“无所畏惧”地做出决定的地区建立更深入的关系，因为中国也派特使前往霍尼亚拉会见新总理杰里米亚·马内莱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 01:31:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-china-seek-bigger-ties-with-solomon-islands-2024-06-06/</guid></item><item><title>诺和诺德准备在中国应对 Ozempic 和 Wegovy 的仿制药挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-braces-generic-challenge-ozempic-wegovy-china-2024-06-05/</link><description>临床试验记录显示，诺和诺德在前景广阔的中国市场面临着日益激烈的竞争，制药商正在开发至少 15 种糖尿病药物 Ozempic 和减肥药物 Wegovy 的仿制药。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 23:06:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-braces-generic-challenge-ozempic-wegovy-china-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>国会批准六月底访问秘鲁后，博卢阿尔特将与中国习近平会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/perus-boluarte-will-meet-chinas-xi-after-congress-oks-late-june-trip-2024-06-05/</link><description>秘鲁总统迪娜·博卢阿特将于本月前往中国，在安第斯国家议会周三批准此行后，会见中国国家主席习近平以及矿业、技术和运输公司的领导人。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 21:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/perus-boluarte-will-meet-chinas-xi-after-congress-oks-late-june-trip-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场回升，中国贸易也回升吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 21:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普试图通过新的 TikTok 策略来吸引年轻男性选民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-seeks-court-young-male-voters-new-tiktok-gambit-2024-06-05/</link><description>两名竞选顾问告诉路透社，唐纳德·特朗普计划在 TikTok 上发布一系列针对年轻人的短片视频，传达有关通货膨胀和其他经济问题的信息，这让人们首次了解这位共和党总统候选人在 2024 年竞选期间对这款受欢迎的应用程序的策略。加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 19:25:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-seeks-court-young-male-voters-new-tiktok-gambit-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国国家电投在巴西风电场投资1.47亿美元并推出太阳能园区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-spic-invests-147-million-brazil-wind-farms-launches-solar-parks-2024-06-05/</link><description>中国电力公司国家电投周三宣布投资7.8亿雷亚尔（1.4741亿美元）在巴西东北部建设两个新风电场，同时在该国太阳能领域首次亮相，两个大型风电场开始运营。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 18:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-spic-invests-147-million-brazil-wind-farms-launches-solar-parks-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫称美国威胁对俄罗斯出口实施制裁，以此勒索中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-us-is-blackmailing-china-by-threatening-sanctions-over-exports-2024-06-05/</link><description>克里姆林宫周三将美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦的言论称为“勒索”，即华盛顿不会容忍中国增加对俄罗斯的“军民两用”商品出口，并将以制裁作为回应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-us-is-blackmailing-china-by-threatening-sanctions-over-exports-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国、“五眼”盟国警告中国招募西方军事训练员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-five-eyes-allies-warn-china-recruiting-western-military-trainers-2024-06-05/</link><description>美国和其他“五眼”国家周三警告说，中国一直在规避旨在停止招募现任和前任西方军事飞行员和其他人员来训练中国军队的措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 17:08:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-five-eyes-allies-warn-china-recruiting-western-military-trainers-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构理事会通过针对伊朗合作和视察员的决议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/iaea-board-governors-passes-resolution-against-iran-diplomats-say-2024-06-05/</link><description>联合国核监督机构的35个国家理事会周三通过了一项决议，呼吁伊朗加强与该监督机构的合作，并撤销最近对视察员的禁令，尽管人们担心德黑兰会以核升级作为回应。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 15:39:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/iaea-board-governors-passes-resolution-against-iran-diplomats-say-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰官员在北京敦促中国参加和平峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukrainian-official-beijing-urges-china-attend-peace-summit-2024-06-05/</link><description>乌克兰第一副外长周三访问中国，并敦促中国派代表团参加计划于本月在瑞士举行的乌克兰峰会，显然希望仍有可能说服中国参加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 14:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukrainian-official-beijing-urges-china-attend-peace-summit-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>帕劳总统称预计中国试图干预选举</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/palau-president-says-he-expects-china-try-meddle-election-2024-06-05/</link><description>太平洋岛国帕劳总统小苏兰杰·惠普斯在接受路透社采访时表示，预计中国将因承认台湾而试图干预今年晚些时候的全国选举。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:32:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/palau-president-says-he-expects-china-try-meddle-election-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>ASML 股价因 CFO Dassen 对订单的评论而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-rise-cfo-dassens-comments-orders-2024-06-05/</link><description>杰富瑞 (Jefferies) 分析师报告引用首席财务官罗杰·达森 (Roger Dassen) 的评论后，阿斯麦 (ASML) 股价周三上涨，该评论表明他对未来几个季度来自最大客户台积电 (TSMC) 的订单可能性持乐观态度。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:30:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-shares-rise-cfo-dassens-comments-orders-2024-06-05/</guid></item><item><title>前新兴世界财政部长呼吁重新调整债务以支持气候支出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/former-emerging-world-finance-chiefs-call-debt-reworks-enable-climate-spending-2024-06-05/</link><description>根据周三发表的一封信，一群著名的前新兴市场金融主管正在敦促全球领导人将外部冲击和气候变化纳入债务可持续性计算中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/former-emerging-world-finance-chiefs-call-debt-reworks-enable-climate-spending-2024-06-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>